reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: i ordered these for work and i really like them. i needed something with lines on the front so i could write notes about the case i have in the file. my only issue is that with the darker colors it is hard to see your writing so i have been sticking with the lighter colors. but that could just be me and my eyesight

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a folder that allowed me to record different data on the cover of the folder. This folder will allow me to record the information I want to and will give me extra lines as well. I also like the various colors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These are well cut and made of a heavy cardstock material so they're durable as well. The colors are nice but the purple and darker blue one are difficult to see writing on so I use a white gel pen on those to solve that issue. I find the design really handy and well done and I'd buy these again for sure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly as Described
reviews.reviewText: These are great file folders, and the notes section comes in handy for jotting down pertinent information.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are good, heavy folders. The lines on the outside are good for making notes. There are 3 of each color - nice for organizing by category. I would purchase these again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Colored Files
reviews.reviewText: I love that this EOOUT files come into multiples colors. It makes finding the correct file so much easier to locate. I also love the fact that you can write on the outside as it comes with lines for notes. I make use of that section on a daily basis, so I do not have to look in the file to see its contents or what I am missing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars The notes space is nice!
reviews.reviewText: There are 8 different colors, with 3 folders each. They seem sturdy and decent quality. I like the fact that I can writes notes on the outside of the folder. The only issue I've had (& why it's not 5 stars) is that 3 of the colors are so dark that notes are not easily readable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: As an accountant, I end up holding onto paperwork that needs more information, to be inputted, only needs to be used short term etc. With these folders, I can write exactly what’s in the folder, reasons why I’m holding onto the paperwork or how long I need to keep it for. Or just for notes about what paperwork is in the folder.These are very helpful and convenient!
